long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Replace your new tab to a clean page with popular useful links, and add a beautiful visual presentation of the current date, day & time!

This extension configures your New Tab page to Super PDF Convert Tab and provides the features below:
- Clean Tab Look
- Popular useful links

Super PDF Convert Tab extension offers easy web search from the Chrome New Tab page. Please note that the extension will change your new tab settings, as well as work and run in the background of your device in order to provide the Services, at all time.
